Steps to Self-Host Fonts

Download URLs
✅ Nunito
Google Fonts page: https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Nunito

Recommended weights:

400 Regular

700 Bold

Click "Download Family" to get all styles, or customize the selection.

✅ Baloo 2
Google Fonts page: https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Baloo+2

Recommended weights:

400 Regular

600 SemiBold

Click "Download Family", or pick only those two weights.

/fonts/
├── Baloo2/
│   ├── Baloo2-Regular.woff2
│   └── Baloo2-SemiBold.woff2
├── Nunito/
│   ├── Nunito-Regular.woff2
│   └── Nunito-Bold.woff2
